        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3194183740" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9903621134146280266">this is a fictionalized biographical novel by Robert Merle. The protagonist, Rudolf Lang, was closely based on the real Rudolf Höß, commandant of the concentration camp Auschwitz. I suggest this book to anyone who wants to know what happen to a person gradually to change him to the monster!</span>

          </span>
        </div>


