        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4002758790" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12947291270458096527">This book might be the best book I have ever read. The style of writing is absolutely captivating. by the time I&apos;m writing this review, about 6 months have passed science reading it, and I still think about this book quite often. Merle does a very good job at describing the character and his inner thoughts. You become quite fond of his character without liking him. It was very interesting because I got to know most of the life and thoughts of this person and yet I didn&apos;t feel sympathy towards hi</span>
  <span id="freeText12947291270458096527" style="display:none">This book might be the best book I have ever read. The style of writing is absolutely captivating. by the time I'm writing this review, about 6 months have passed science reading it, and I still think about this book quite often. Merle does a very good job at describing the character and his inner thoughts. You become quite fond of his character without liking him. It was very interesting because I got to know most of the life and thoughts of this person and yet I didn't feel sympathy towards him (which is very important when we read about a real person who did horrible things).<br /><br />I can only recommend this book.</span>
  <a data-text-id="12947291270458096527" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

